### Variables (shared across all .http files)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@accessToken = 
@refreshToken = 
@userToken = 
@userRefreshToken = 
@userId = 
@requestId = 

### ─── Users (Admin) ───

### List users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Change user role
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "MODERATOR"
}

### Change user status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "SUSPENDED"
}

### ─── Uploader Requests ───

### Request uploader status (any logged-in user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/me/uploader-request
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### List pending uploader requests (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/uploader-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Direct approve uploader by user ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/approve-uploader
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Approve uploader request (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/uploader-requests/{{requestId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Reject uploader request (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/uploader-requests/{{requestId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
